<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Two pieces of a <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">sundial</rs>—not certainly both from the same monument. a: two joining fragments without edges (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.21</measure> across cord × <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.34</measure>   × <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.20</measure>); b: fragment with lower rim (<measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.26</measure> across cord × <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.52</measure>   × <measure dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.175</measure>).</p>
</div>
